'''Leafpad'''是一个[[开放源代码|开源]]的[[文本编辑器|文本编辑器]]，适用于[[Linux|Linux]]、[[BSD|BSD]]和[[Maemo|Maemo]]。着重于创建一个轻量级的文本编辑器且[[数据依赖|依赖]]最少，它的设计简单，易于编译。Leafpad是[[LXDE|LXDE]]<ref name="LXDE">{{cite web |url=http://lxde.sourceforge.net/about.html |title=LXDE - Lightweight X11 Desktops Environment |date=30 April 2008 |work=LXDE Project |publisher=Sourceforge |accessdate=18 October 2011 |archive-date=2012-10-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121010112452/http://lxde.sourceforge.net/about.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>及[[Xubuntu|Xubuntu]] 11.10<ref name="Xubuntu11.10">{{cite web |url=https://wiki.ubuntu.com/Xubuntu/OneiricOcelot/Final |title=Information about Xbuntu 11.10 |date=13 October 2011 |work=Ubuntu Wiki |publisher=Ubuntu |accessdate=18 October 2011 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120105034741/https://wiki.ubuntu.com/Xubuntu/OneiricOcelot/Final |archivedate=2012年1月5日 }}</ref>和12.04<ref name="Xubuntu12.04">{{cite web |url=http://xubuntu.org/news/12-04-release/ |title=Xubuntu 12.04 released |date=26 April 2012 |publisher=Canonical |accessdate=26 April 2012 |archive-date=2020-11-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201111183449/https://xubuntu.org/news/12-04-release/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>上的默认的文本编辑器。

Leafpad是[[自由软件|自由软件]]，依据[[GNU通用公共许可证|GNU通用公共许可证]]的条款发布。<ref name=leafpad>{{cite web |url=http://tarot.freeshell.org/leafpad/ |title=Leafpad |date=23 December 2010 |work=tarot.freeshell.org |accessdate=18 October 2011 |archive-date=2016-10-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161003124941/http://tarot.freeshell.org/leafpad/ }}</ref>

== 功能 ==

Leafpad的功能包括[[字符编码|字符编码]]选项，自动字符编码检测，无限撤销/重做功能<ref name="LinuxInsider">{{cite web |url=http://www.linuxinsider.com/story/69703.html |title=gEdit and Leafpad Make a Good Text-Editing Team |author=Jack M. Germain |date=7 April 2010 |work=LinuxInsider |accessdate=18 October 2011 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120331030036/http://www.linuxinsider.com/story/69703.html |archive-date=2012-03-31 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>，及拖放功能<ref name="ghacks">{{cite web |url=http://www.ghacks.net/2010/05/01/leafpad-yet-another-linux-text-editor/ |title=Leafpad: Yet another Linux text editor |author=Jack Wallen |date=1 May 2010 |work=ghacks.net |accessdate=18 October 2011 |archive-date=2020-11-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201125135209/https://www.ghacks.net/2010/05/01/leafpad-yet-another-linux-text-editor/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

与其它编辑器，如[[Gedit|Gedit]]或[[Kate|Kate]]相比，Leafpad[[内存占用|内存占用]]较小<ref name="LinuxInsider"/><ref name="MakeUseOf">{{cite web |url=http://www.makeuseof.com/tag/leafpad-ultralightweight-text-editor-linux/ |title=Leafpad – An Ultra-Lightweight Text Editor |author=Danny Stieben |date=2 May 2011 |work=MakeUseOf |accessdate=18 October 2011 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111110081606/http://www.makeuseof.com/tag/leafpad-ultralightweight-text-editor-linux/ |archive-date=2011-11-10 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

